1. *Morala* je da se zahvalim na poklonu. (She had to thank for the gift.)

2. Nisam *morala* da odem. (I didn't have to go.)

3. On je znao da neće *morati* da čeka dugo. (He knew he wouldn't have to wait long.)

4. Nećemo *morati* da čekamo dugo. (We won't have to wait long.)

5. *Morali* su da se suoče sa istinom. (They had to face the truth.)

6. *Morala* je da se suoči sa istinom. (She had to face the truth.)